Task 3: Create the View

The university wants only eligible students visible.

Conditions:

marks > 80

attendance > 85

CREATE VIEW eligible_scholarship_students AS
SELECT student_id, name, department, marks, attendance
FROM students
WHERE marks > 80 AND attendance > 85;  

